{"id":231833119,"title":"在英國意外入手大象杯","content":"這幾天去Bristol 參加熱氣球節\n陰晴不定的天氣無法親眼看到熱氣球\n在Park street 吃完午餐後想喝珍珠奶茶\n\n找到這家Jo’s tea 看到這個杯子似曾相似\n想著最近英國天氣熱很常買冰咖啡而造成的垃圾量\n加上這個杯子有吸管而且有蓋子防側漏（？）\n店家還免費送一杯任選飲料，就結帳了😘\n\n\nhttps://i.imgur.com/Prc0z66.jpg\n\n看了外盒的介紹才勾起記憶\n這就是前陣子看到募資的大象杯呢\n在遠離家鄉的英國看見台灣人的設計著實感動\n\n這幾天帶到咖啡廳每位店員都很好奇\n點中杯cold brew結果店員都幫我加滿到700ml 🙈","excerpt":"這幾天去Bristol 參加熱氣球節，陰晴不定的天氣無法親眼看到熱氣球，在Park street 吃完午餐後想喝珍珠奶茶，找到這家Jo’s tea 看到這個杯子似曾相似，想著最近英國天氣熱很常買冰咖啡","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"49eed176-a7ad-492c-b6cf-77733ab633ef","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-08-10T14:45:34.907Z","updatedAt":"2019-08-10T14:45:34.907Z","commentCount":31,"likeCount":625,"tags":[],"topics":[],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"無痕生活","forumAlias":"ecolife","school":"中國文化大學","department":"資訊傳播學系","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":null,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":622},{"id":"e8e6bc5d-41b0-4129-b134-97507523d7ff","count":2},{"id":"aa0d425f-d530-4478-9a77-fe3aedc79eea","count":1}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/Prc0z66.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"ccb9f19f-456c-4610-960b-01a36737f40b","url":"https://i.imgur.com/Prc0z66l.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/Prc0z66l.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/Prc0z66l.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-08-10T14:45:34.907Z","updatedAt":"2019-08-10T14:45:34.907Z"},{"id":"ccb9f19f-456c-4610-960b-01a36737f40b","url":"https://i.imgur.com/Prc0z66.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/Prc0z66","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/Prc0z66l.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-08-10T14:45:34.907Z","updatedAt":"2019-08-10T14:45:34.907Z"}],"postAvatar":""}